        <div type="letter">
            <div type="text">
                <opener>
                    <placeName>Down Bromley Kent [4 Chester Place]</placeName>
                    <date>March 31<hi rend="superscript">st</hi></date>
                    <salute>Dear &amp; Respected Sir</salute>
                </opener>
                <div type="transcription">
                     
<p>I thank you sincerely for your kind note &amp; truly magnificent present of your great work on the Geology of the Novara expedition.<ref target="#foot.f2"/> No doubt I shall in due time receive it safely &amp; shall valueit highly.— I have always watched your progress, as shown by extracts in various scientific Journals, with great interest, &amp; I most fully appreciate how much valuable work you have performed in the good cause of natural Science.—</p>
<p>With sincere respect &amp; cordial thanks, I remain | Dear Sir,</p>
<p>Yours very faithfully | Charles Darwin</p> 
                </div>
            </div>
            <div type="tnotes">
                <note xml:id="tnote.n1">1.3 value] <hi rend="italic">after omitted point</hi> </note>
            </div>

            
            
            
            
            
        </div>

        

        

